media:group.media:title: [HcUim 22] Back after a 3 year hiatus
media:group.media:description:
Regular UIM with 2 additional rules: 
- No looting bag
- No death storage

So if I happen to die to e.g. Vorkath, I'll have to discard everything that is in the death storage.
Good thing this account is basically a skiller tho.
